                        <p style="margin-top: 0.12cm;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span lang="es-ES-u-co-trad"><strong>NUEVAS TAREAS (EXTRA PLANES)</strong></span></span></span></p>
